    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/223a18-2/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=605717717370012570&sectionId=605717717470806938)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUYRw8nmHu_text","label":"ggUYRw8nmHu_text","default":"Discover why 40,000+ busy moms are waking up to 'Glass Skin' and a refreshed glow with this 3-hour Bio-Collagen Reset"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMTtLiPXuX_text","label":"ggMTtLiPXuX_text","default":"<p>By Nicole Jenkins | UK<br>February, 2026</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggy5Uy9f896_text","label":"ggy5Uy9f896_text","default":"<p>Most moms don’t skip skincare because they don’t care. They skip it because there’s no energy left at the end of the day. <strong>Between work, kids, and everything in between, long routines just aren’t realistic; even when your skin clearly needs help.</strong></p><p><br>That’s why more busy moms are turning to overnight skincare that works in the background, while they rest.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj-b7-Ufnz_text","label":"ggj-b7-Ufnz_text","default":"Here are the 7 reasons why I’ve actually stuck with it:"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZHuYgoc8x_text","label":"ggZHuYgoc8x_text","default":"1. It actually stays put while you live your life"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvDN5djePx_text","label":"ggvDN5djePx_text","default":"<p>Most masks are just \"wet paper\" that slides off the second you stand up. This Bio-Collagen mask acts like a second skin. You can do the laundry, cook dinner, or even sleep in it without a single drip. It’s <strong>\"Passive Skincare\"</strong>, it does the hard work while you’re busy being a mom.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNzvrSfCrV_text","label":"ggNzvrSfCrV_text","default":"2. One mask replaces a 5-step routine"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxwUzin72S_text","label":"ggxwUzin72S_text","default":"<p>Stop overcomplicating things. You don't need a shelf full of serums that don't sink in. <strong>One Nifora session provides deeper hydration than a whole week of standard moisturizers.</strong> It saves you time, money, and cabinet space.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjPk9bJpvM_text","label":"ggjPk9bJpvM_text","default":"3. No More \"Mom Face\" Fatigue"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUrpHf4v9e_text","label":"ggUrpHf4v9e_text","default":"<p>We’ve all had those weeks where we look in the mirror and just feel... tired. <strong>This ritual is like an \"Undo\" button for dullness.</strong> It rebuilds that bouncy, healthy texture so you look like you’ve actually caught up on sleep, even when you’re running on empty.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7nCPFUnoD_label","label":"gg7nCPFUnoD_label","default":"<p>CHECK AVAILABILITY</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQPtwZzMvG_text","label":"ggQPtwZzMvG_text","default":"4. It’s like a \"blanket\" that presses the glow into your skin"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxpEEAWkOo_text","label":"ggxpEEAWkOo_text","default":"<p>Most creams just sit on the surface and evaporate into the air. This mask acts like a little blanket for your face. It creates <strong>an airtight seal that \"presses\" the hydration deep into your pores</strong> instead of letting it dry out on your pillowcase.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHIzq54zz__text","label":"ggHIzq54zz__text","default":"5. The \"Transparency Test\"—You can see it working"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQ78Sg6Zrx_text","label":"ggQ78Sg6Zrx_text","default":"<p>You don’t have to guess if this is doing anything. The mask starts off as a thick, milky white. <strong>As your skin \"drinks\" up the ingredients, the mask becomes 100% transparent.</strong> When it’s clear, you know the nutrients have successfully moved from the mask into your skin. It’s the most satisfying visual proof you’ll ever see in your routine.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOkzpODfF8_text","label":"ggOkzpODfF8_text","default":"6. It’s a \"Retinol Reset\" without the redness"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3BajX3jAe_text","label":"gg3BajX3jAe_text","default":"<p>If your skin is sensitive or reactive, \"new\" products can be scary. This hydrogel is cooling and ultra-gentle. <strong>It calms redness and smooths texture without the burning or stinging you get from harsh acids or chemical peels.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTCZJLSmNN_text","label":"ggTCZJLSmNN_text","default":"7. You can try the \"Glow\" Risk-Free"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOGc25WEdF_text","label":"ggOGc25WEdF_text","default":"<p>We know you've probably been burned by viral gimmicks before. <strong>That’s why Nifora offers a 60-day satisfaction guarantee.</strong> If you don't see that \"glass skin\" bounce after your first few resets, you aren't stuck with it.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUMmUh3HgV_label","label":"ggUMmUh3HgV_label","default":"<p>CHECK AVAILABILITY</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggd-lhkHKNI_text","label":"ggd-lhkHKNI_text","default":"<p><strong>Note from the Warehouse:</strong> Because we make our collagen in small, high-potency batches, we frequently sell out during the winter months. If the link above works, it means we currently have stock ready to ship!</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghX7bwbbYs_label","label":"gghX7bwbbYs_label","default":"<p>CHECK AVAILABILITY</p>"}],
